{"tid":969424,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［惡搞品牌］是咁的 我為所有環保L搞左個時裝品牌","createTime":"2019-01-05T05:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T08:02:28.000Z","uid":21863,"like":249,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b6c7d27d26b6806056b68ef44940c1cc97234e9a","tid":969424,"uid":21863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T05:08:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，見近排咁多人整時裝品牌，我都心血來潮係屋企一個人創立左個二次創作同惡搞為主嘅品牌。<br />\n<br />\n既然近期環保風氣盛行，我一於先為所有環保人士整件連登狗pocket tee 宣揚走飲筒意識！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TcqdOLb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcqdOLb.png&h=3f866d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n著住去食m記、大家樂就岩晒，見到經理真係無比飲筒，即刻可以拉低個pocket 支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHYSjRR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHYSjRR.png&h=f77d3d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一件作品其實係惡搞好多潮童吹捧既 RIPNDIP 中指貓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9aNdHG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9aNdHG.png&h=8b3a251f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外一件 全部都要 t-shirt ，參考早前連登流行的簡化圖創作... <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bsw05NP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbsw05NP.png&h=f7baa640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果搵到7fargo男神代言，個感覺大概會係咁⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tt0AUGL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftt0AUGL.png&h=39be92c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左衫，都ff下其他產品先。<br />\nIG 女神princejoyce 馬克杯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XzTF5OC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXzTF5OC.png&h=95b981b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7j9qxtD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7j9qxtD.png&h=81bef4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2uMAafj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2uMAafj.png&h=2c3da86a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦，既然有設計，咁點都要整返個品牌名同logo。我決定簡個潮d既名 －  9ITEM<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmdCvYP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmdCvYP.png&h=1eceb997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇小個logo，我都花左半個鐘設計。為左表現文藝復興時期的美術哲學，過程中參考大師達文西繪畫蒙羅麗莎時使用1：1.618的黃金比例。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sd9Rs02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSd9Rs02.png&h=e0f62071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都照舊講下挫折...第一件衫其實係我琴日係m記飲可樂無飲筒，敏感牙齒激發我諗出黎。當中既痛楚同辛酸，相信好多巴絲都感受過。<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果你想支持呢個品牌/睇多d創作，可以follow facebook 同 instagram<br />\nig: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/9item/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F9item%2F&d=T1%2FbvXP8%2Bo0cJI4QM9OX25ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=eb304403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/9item/</a><br />\nfb：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/9ITEM.OFFICIAL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F9ITEM.OFFICIAL&d=T1%2FbvXP8%2Bo0cJI4QM9OX25ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d29b1040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/9ITEM.OFFICIAL</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評：設計幾盞鬼支持！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評：二次創作﹑惡搞即係抄，應該收皮"},{"pid":"812bf3ac6a437d40f92fb72549013e20b1a619e1","tid":969424,"uid":7656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T05:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951a299f5be21ffdcecad9ff4422abd94a2b5d46","tid":969424,"uid":84472,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"叫連仔包起嚟條啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class